data.description: Don't miss out on your opportunity to call Bradley Estates home! Fresh paint and new carpeting compliment the original hardwood floors throughout this three bedroom ranch. Fully applianced kitchen features dark wood cabinetry and granite countertops. Living room with crown moulding and huge picture window. Lower level awaits finishing but has new bracing and drain tile for your peace of mind! Fenced backyard and large side yard. Two car garage and long driveway gives ample room for all your toys!
